  The card enters play as if just cast and you get to make all necessary
    decisions from scratch. [Visions FAQ 02/16/97]

  Any X in the casting cost is zero since it is not actually being cast.
    [DeLaney 02/02/97]

 @{" Card Information " link VI_BLUE.guide/DESER}

@endnode
@node DNOMA "Desert Nomads"

@{b}Desert Nomads@{ub}

