    tap a land that turn. [bethmo 02/13/97]

  It only works if Desolation is in play at the end of the turn.
    [bethmo 02/26/97]

 @{" Card Information " link VI_BLACK.guide/DESOL}

@endnode
@node DESPE "Desperate Gambit"

@{b}Desperate Gambit@{ub}

  This is played during damage prevention.  You must choose the damage from
    the source you want to affect when you announce the spell, which is before
    the flip. [D'Angelo 06/12/97]

 @{" Card Information " link WL_RED.guide/DESPE}

@endnode
